  ('Bob Cut', 'Haircuts', 'Classic, timeless bob cut with precision layers for movement and shine. Perfect for all face shapes.', 60, 3200, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611090626919-30bda6c22402?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80'),
