  ('Layer Cut', 'Haircuts', 'Multi-layered cut with volume at the crown. Creates movement, texture, and dimension throughout.', 75, 3800, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1595477360723-a25a6c6bc8d2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80'),
