  ('V-Cut', 'Haircuts', 'V-shaped layers that converge at the back. Elongates face, adds flow, and creates beautiful movement.', 70, 3400, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1599623531885-5c3d8d6dd1d3?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80'),
